---

---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-highlight font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-3">About</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          From enterprise systems to empowering businesses
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I'm Amr Sarhan, a Principal ERP &amp; Human Capital Management Specialist based in
          Dubai, UAE. Over the past 12+ years, I've worked with organizations ranging from
          government authorities and national banks to petroleum companies and healthcare
          institutions — across the UAE, Saudi Arabia, Egypt, Kuwait, Qatar, Oman, Ghana, and South Africa.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          My career took me from Vodafone through Oracle itself, and now into senior consulting
          roles where I lead HCM implementations, ERP upgrades, and digital transformation
          initiatives for major enterprises.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Now I'm channeling that expertise into helping businesses of all sizes digitalize
          their operations, automate their workflows, and build the systems they need to
          scale and thrive.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">12+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Years of Experience</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">20+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Enterprise Clients</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">8</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Countries Served</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills / Expertise -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-6">Core Expertise</h3>
        {[
          { skill: "Oracle Fusion HCM Cloud", level: "98%" },
          { skill: "Oracle EBS (HR, Payroll, SSHR, AME)", level: "96%" },
          { skill: "SQL / PL/SQL / OTBI Reporting", level: "94%" },
          { skill: "Global Payroll & RetroPay", level: "92%" },
          { skill: "Implementation & Data Migration", level: "90%" },
        ].map(({ skill, level }) => (
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-dark">{skill}</span>
              <span class="text-muted">{level}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-full"
                style={`width: ${level}`}
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
